{"tid":1175349,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"近世沒有一個極權國家的政權的壽命超過七十年","createTime":"2019-05-28T13:11:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-28T14:54:44.000Z","uid":22675,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"5cb05106bfd9c7096fd3096bb16cc3a7df095d1c","tid":1175349,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T13:11:36.000Z","msg":"中華人民共和國的壽命將有多長？<br />\n（我在三年前寫的一篇舊作）<br />\n<br />\n冇人能確切地回答這問題，但我的直覺是它的壽命應該不會超過70年（或只有70年）。將來的歷史書上是這樣記載：中華人民共和國（1949-2019），這是因為到目前為止，近世仍沒有一個極權國家的政權的壽命超過七十年。前蘇聯是由1922年至1991年的，亦即只有69年。第二個原因是因為中共內鬥嚴重，現在仍在進行中，冇人知道內鬥的結果將會是怎樣。第三是中國經濟可能在不久將來崩潰，這是因為國內不良貸款太多，遲早爆煲。但所有這些，都是不足夠令中共垮台的，所以，我的預測（夢想）能否成真，仍是未知之數。（最新發展：中美貿易戰可能升級成為冷戰，到時，中共命更危。）"},{"pid":"84253165ac612b26a00c2a8ba221294b2f90039b","tid":1175349,"uid":22675,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T13:12:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nx2TKTH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNx2TKTH.png&h=c11f8216&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/LamCheng/permalink/763340187395156?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2FLamCheng%2Fpermalink%2F763340187395156%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=AW73mzr4JVDAANnbo7Up2LVsU2rIM%2B0kfQ6zMqXKyqM%3D&h=15b74472\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/LamCheng/permalink/763340187395156?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"0bff347b07446871ff574d4bc6b65ce9ecb0bc33","tid":1175349,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T13:27:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f0b84d02fdd3ac954b2efd98c18cad41f247dbb","tid":1175349,"uid":165336,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T13:32:49.000Z","msg":"我覺得起碼仲有20年玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11f9b856a0fe653246cfc838989b12726622e372","tid":1175349,"uid":133680,"like":22,"d